<task id="connecting_with_hdmi">
    <title>使用HDMI线进行投屏</title>
    <shortdesc>使用HDMI线可以实现稳定与清晰度的投屏。</shortdesc>
    <taskbody>
        <prereq id="prereq_bnq_qxx_3dc">需要准备Type-c转HDMI转接头</prereq>
        <context>
            <p></p>
        </context>
        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd>将HDMI线与转接头相联</cmd>
                <info>注意HDMI接口的朝向。</info>
                <stepresult><image href="image/stepresult.png" id="image_rqy_jyx_3dc"/></stepresult>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>将转接头的Type-C端口与iPad的Type-C端口相连</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>将控制台的信号输入源切换为笔记本输入。</cmd>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
    <related-links>
        <link href="mirror_your_ipad_with_airplay.dita" format="xml"/>
    </related-links>
</task>
